               <p>SECOND COUNT - stating it to be the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120219-55-victim509" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Ranyard
                  <interp inst="t18120219-55-victim509" type="surname" value="Ranyard"></interp>
